                <div class="entry-body">		
                    <br><br> <h3 class="title"><a href="">Introduction</a></h3><br>
                    <p align ="justify">
                        This is the prime event of the ‘Are You Ready?’ programme. The employers are given the opportunity to interview the skillful and resourceful undergraduates of the university. This is a great opportunity for the industry to have a first look at the skilled and innovative undergraduates of one of the best engineering university of the country. In turn the undergraduates will get a valuable opportunity to collaborate with the industrial representatives. The ability to face an interview as a trial is a great opportunity for all the undergraduates which will be very much helpful in the coming years. </p>


                    <br> <h3 class="title"><a href="">Content</a></h3><br>

                    <ul>







                        <li>• Mock or Real interviews will be conducted in a manner that it would be very beneficial for the students for future endeavours.
                        </li><li></li>
                        <li>• The performance of the interviewees will be evaluated and presented then and there, in order for the undergraduates to assess their performances.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <br><br/>
                    <br> <h4>Date</h4>20th of December 2013<br>
                    <br> <h4>Time</h4>8:00 AM<br>


                    <br>




                </div><!--/ .entry-body-->

